      • create

        public static long create(java.lang.String hash,
                          java.lang.String deviceName,
                          java.lang.String interfaceIP,
                          java.lang.String interfaceMAC,
                          java.lang.String osVersion,
                          java.lang.String nmapVersion,
                          RequestStatus status,
                          java.util.Date timeReceived)
                   throws DaoException
        Creates a new request using the data provided and caches it.
        Parameters:
        hash - the agent's hash value.
        deviceName - the agent's device name.
        interfaceIP - the agent's interface IP address.
        interfaceMAC - the agent's interface MAC address.
        osVersion - the agent's operating system version.
        nmapVersion - the agent's nmap version.
        status - the request's status.
        timeReceived - time the request was received.
        Returns:
        the newly created request's id or 0 if the request could not be retrieved for caching after its creation.
        Throws:
        DaoException - if the request could not be created or retrieved for caching.
